These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, october, february
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, onion, apple
3 different games are played: billiard, backgammon, mah-jongg
1. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person eating apple##1
2. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking milk##2
4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person eating apple is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Birthday         | october | may   | february   |
| Beverage   | tea     | coffee | milk |
| Food   | apple  | asparagus    | onion      |
| Game     | backgammon     | billiard      | mah-jongg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, security-guard, videographer
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, mirinda, coffee
3 different games are played: chess, canasta, billiard
City: nizza, liverpool, berlin
1. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the security-guard is the person playing billiard##1
4. the engineer is the person playing canasta##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is between the person drinking mirinda and the videographer##2
6. the videographer is the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Job          | security-guard  | engineer     | videographer     |
| Beverage   | mirinda     | coffee     | water      |
| Game   | billiard  | canasta | chess |
| City           | berlin | nizza     | liverpool       |

