.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
House: wooden, art-deco, craftsman
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, jet-ski, car
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, rose, orchid
City: edinburgh, miami, paris
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person driving the car and the person who growsorchid##2
3. the wooden house is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to miami is the art-deco house##1
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| House          | wooden  | craftsman     | art-deco     |
| Transport           | car | train  | jet-ski   |
| Flower   | daffodil  | rose    | orchid |
| City           | paris     | edinburgh | miami |

