.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, scooter, car
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, january, february
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, mauve, white
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, water, soy-milk
1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person driving the car is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who likes ivory##2
4. the person driving the scooter is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Transport    | helicopter       | car  | scooter   |
| Birthday     | january    | february  | october |
| Color     | mauve   | white | ivory        |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | 7up     | water      |

