.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, cricket, baseball
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, september, may
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, librarian, musician
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, nigerian, malaysian
1. the musician is on the left of the librarian##1
2. the indonesian is between the musician and the person who's birthday is in may##2
3. the person who's birthday is in march is the nigerian##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the indonesian is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Sport          | baseball    | soccer     | cricket      |
| Birthday         | march | september | may |
| Job   | musician  | librarian       | electrician       |
| Nationality           | nigerian     | indonesian       | malaysian     |

