.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, august, june
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, pall-mall, old-henry
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, poppy, marigold
City: colone, paris, hannover
1. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
2. the pall-mall-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person traveling to colone##2
3. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person traveling to colone is on the far right##1
5. the pall-mall-smoker is between the old-henry-smoker and the person who growstulip##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Birthday          | june      | august   | october |
| Cigar         | dannemann | pall-mall | old-henry |
| Flower   | tulip      | marigold | poppy   |
| City     | hannover         | paris  | colone       |

