.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
There 3 different types of food: lemon, mango, pear
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, parkour, climbing
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, light-blue, lilac
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, mystery, fantasy
1. the person who likes lilac is on the far left##1
2. the person eating mango is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person eating mango is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person who likes white is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person eating pear##2
5. the person eating mango is the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Food      | lemon       | mango      | pear      |
| Sport         | parkour    | climbing | ice-hockey      |
| Color           | lilac | white     | light-blue |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery     | fantasy          | scientific       |

