.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-9::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, bongani, baccarat
3 different pets are kept: bird, goat, mouse
3 different games are played: billiard, snooker, whist
City: boston, hamburg, new-york
1. the person traveling to new-york is between the person playing snooker and the person playing whist##2
2. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
3. the blend-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
5. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
6. the person traveling to hamburg is the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Cigar      | blend      | bongani | baccarat     |
| Pet          | goat   | bird      | mouse     |
| Game   | whist  | billiard      | snooker |
| City     | boston | new-york        | hamburg     |

