.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-10::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, aconite, zinnia
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, chaman, cain
There 3 different types of food: banana, pineapple, grapefruit
House: modern, ranch-style, gothic-revival
1. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
2. the chaman-smoker is between the fonseca-smoker and the person who growsaconite##2
3. the person eating grapefruit is the person who growszinnia##1
4. the person eating pineapple is the cain-smoker##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
6. the modern house is the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Flower       | aconite       | zinnia       | sunflower    |
| Cigar         | cain | chaman | fonseca |
| Food       | pineapple      | grapefruit         | banana |
| House   | modern        | gothic-revival            | ranch-style  |

