.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-11::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, golf, swimming
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, purple, turquise
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, cain, tiparillo
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, guinea-pig, bird
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is in the middle##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person who likes purple and the person who likes red##2
5. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the person who likes red is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Sport      | swimming     | golf | surfing      |
| Color         | purple  | turquise       | red |
| Cigar   | tiparillo   | cain         | bongani     |
| Pet   | goldfish | guinea-pig    | bird     |

