2. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
5. the person eating cranberry is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who growsbegonia##2
6. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Food      | blueberry | cranberry      | watermelon            |
| Birthday           | february | may | august |
| Flower   | begonia     | daisy        | daffodil         |
| Sport   | parkour  | soccer    | biathlon        |

