.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-13::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, singing, gardening
There 3 different types of food: avocado, papaya, grapes
City: berlin, new-york, venice
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, r&b, hip-hop
1. the fan hip-hop is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person eating grapes and the person traveling to venice##2
4. the fan r&b is on the left of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Hobby           | photography | singing        | gardening       |
| Food   | avocado | papaya | grapes |
| City           | venice     | new-york         | berlin  |
| Music-Genre         | r&b  | hip-hop       | rock  |

