.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-14::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, soccer, cricket
3 different games are played: whist, billiard, bridge
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, jet-ski, trike
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, rat, goldfish
1. the person who's sport is cricket is between the owner of the rat and the person playing bridge##2
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the person playing whist is the owner of the rat##1
6. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Sport      | soccer    | cricket          | badminton |
| Game          | bridge | billiard           | whist        |
| Transport           | jet-ski | trike | train         |
| Pet   | rabbit    | goldfish    | rat      |

