The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, photography, hiking
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, daffodil, sunflower
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, june, august
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who growssunflower##2
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person traveling to paris##2
5. the person who's hobby is photography is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| City          | new-york  | marseilles   | paris |
| Hobby   | hiking  | photography     | fishing |
| Flower   | rose | daffodil | sunflower   |
| Birthday     | august   | june   | december      |

