There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, french, argentine
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, journalist, social-worker
3 different games are played: domino, chess, bridge
1. the french is on the right of the person playing chess##1
2. the argentine is between the person playing domino and the spanish##2
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
4. the journalist is the person playing domino##1
5. the social-worker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Birthday       | february | may | december |
| Nationality         | spanish   | argentine       | french        |
| Job       | social-worker | electrician   | journalist         |
| Game   | bridge    | chess     | domino         |

