.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-17::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, water
3 different games are played: monopoly, whist, canasta
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, radish, spinach
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, parkour, biathlon
1. the person playing whist is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person playing monopoly##2
2. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the person drinking fanta is the person eating eggplant##1
4. the person eating spinach is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is the person eating radish##1
6. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Beverage   | fanta | hot-chocolate  | water     |
| Game   | canasta    | whist | monopoly |
| Food           | eggplant        | spinach   | radish  |
| Sport     | biathlon      | parkour   | rowing |

