.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-18::.
3 different games are played: monopoly, chess, billiard
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, scooter, bus
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, february, august
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, rowing, cycling
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person driving the bus is the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person playing chess is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
6. the person playing billiard is between the person playing monopoly and the person who's birthday is in february##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Game           | chess   | billiard   | monopoly |
| Transport   | bus | scooter   | bike     |
| Birthday   | february     | december      | august    |
| Sport           | rugby | rowing | cycling    |

