.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, cycling, weightlifting
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, animation, martial-arts
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, february, may
3 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon, poker
1. the person playing backgammon is the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person watching family movies##2
4. the person who's birthday is in february is the person playing poker##1
5. the person playing monopoly is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's birthday is in february##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Sport      | snowboarding | weightlifting     | cycling        |
| Movie-Genre         | animation   | martial-arts | family |
| Birthday   | february        | march       | may      |
| Game           | poker           | monopoly    | backgammon       |

