.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
House: gothic-revival, ranch-style, tower
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, adventure, horror
3 different games are played: go, snooker, billiard
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, polish, turkish
1. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is the nigerian##1
3. the person playing snooker is the nigerian##1
4. the person playing go is the tower house##1
5. the person watching horror movies is between the turkish and the person playing snooker##2
6. the person playing billiard is the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| House        | ranch-style      | gothic-revival | tower |
| Movie-Genre         | adventure     | horror    | epic        |
| Game       | snooker | billiard   | go   |
| Nationality   | nigerian          | polish     | turkish       |

 